Sentence: For GA as an outcome, the model contained MMP - 2, VEGF, ICAM - 1 and ET - 1, and the optimal model for the IBW / GA ratio was composed of maternal plasma BET - 1, MMP - 2 and - 9, VEGF and BMI.
